cleaner-wanted.title: CLEANER WANTED
pars:
We are currently seeking a
dedicated cleaner to
work locally in Rushworth.
Approx 23 hours per fortnight –
afternoons from 3.30pm
(or early morning) MON-FRI

Experience preferred but not essential
– energy and positive
attitude a must.

Please forward resume or enquires
to Trudie
trudie@kycleaningservice.com.au
